Description
Can you invoke help flags for a tool or binary? This program has extraordinarily helpful information...

$ wget https://mercury.picoctf.net/static/beec4f433e5ee5bfcd71bba8d5863faf/warm



Run this program by entering the following in the Terminal prompt: $ ./warm, but you'll first have to make it executable with $ chmod +x warm (+x macht es executable)

